{"tid":1842243,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【緊急！唔夠人！】聯署！幫美國對冧中共，等於幫香港！","createTime":"2020-01-25T14:51:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T14:54:28.000Z","uid":346341,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a98bc5080358b09ea07e2c54c1dc1a5471fc4b4b","tid":1842243,"uid":346341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T14:51:31.000Z","msg":"作為和理非／鍵盤戰士嘅你！唔該可唔可以花少少時間幫我簽一簽個名？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Link： <a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fappeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJS1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=492cc609\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china</a></span></span><br />\n聯署呼籲在中美第二階段協議加入香港真雙普選<br />\n仲要多三萬個簽名，但係淨係得返五日咋！！！（截止日期：二月一日）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n侵侵前幾日指中美第二階段協議會同中國人權問題同埋香港民主問題有關：<br />\n經濟日報報導： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/38D5FUl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F38D5FUl&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJS1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=d4577963\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/38D5FUl</a><br />\n<blockquote>特朗普在瑞士達沃斯世界經濟論壇的記者會上，被問及會否把<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人權</span></span></strong>納入第二階段中美貿易協議內。<br />\n特朗普回應指︰<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我們已在討論這個問題，我們會希望我們可在此做點事。</span></span></strong><br />\n特朗普又指︰<br />\n我們正在談貿易協議，而這是非常大的協議。第一階段已完成，而第二階段正在開始，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我們亦會討論人權問題。</span></span></strong><br />\n特朗普又在記者會上談及，中方承諾未來2年額外購買2,000億美元的美國貨品。特朗普形容，這數字可隨着時間增加。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n侵侵知道香港係中共要嚟攞美金嘅要地，所以。我哋要配合美國，從中得到雙普選，令到中共連香港呢個春袋都無埋！（隨時中共滅亡都有可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n有雙普選 = 由新（由人民選出來，更有公信力）政府 = 容易達到五大訴求 = 無辜負手足嘅期望！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />CCPig<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n天滅中共！光復香港！"},{"pid":"51e670dcec76b622289e7ae3eaf5db1458f0d838","tid":1842243,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T14:54:28.000Z","msg":"推"}]}